    "Generate code to create a chart(V1): In this step,you'll prompt an LLM to write Pythoncode that generates a chart in response to a user query about the coffee dataset. The dataset includes field such as date, coffee_type, quantity, and revenue and you will pass the schema into the LLM so it knows what data is available.\n",
